   "source": [
    "## Running a bunch of simulation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b47739e1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Just craft a list of the parameters you would like to run and use the `parallel_compute` function."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "1b00593a",
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2024-02-28T17:53:08.844605Z",
     "start_time": "2024-02-28T17:52:12.519409Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from slotted_aloha_simulator.parallel import parallel_compute\n",
    "p_list = [{'p0': p, 'n': 2**i, 't_sim': 20, 'alpha': 1/2, 'm': 12} for p in [1/8, 1/4, 1/2, 3/4] \n",
    "          for i in range(1, 11)]\n",
    "data = parallel_compute(p_list)"
   ]
